ties and mass-function of the post-starburst\ngalaxies are consistent with a scenario in which gas-rich mergers contribute to\nthe growth of the low and intermediate mass range of the red sequence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2014 15:23:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
